comment: The ball gets stuck between the rim and the backboard, resulting in a jump ball at the center circle. Any two players who were in the game at the time of the event are eligible to jump for their team.
Moore (CHI) makes slight contact with Westbrook's (OKC) arm after he releases the ball, but does not affect his ability to follow-through.
Brooks (CHI) splits the double team on the drive to the basket and dives to the ground while attempting the layup.
Kanter (OKC) cleanly knocks the ball away from Mirotic (CHI) as he attempts his layup.
Moore (CHI) disrupts Westbrook's (OKC) RSBQ as he drives toward the basket.
Westbrook (OKC) steps over the plane of the free throw line before the ball touches the basket ring.
Gasol (CHI) sets the screen on Roberson (OKC) and gives him the opportunity to stop and/or change direction.
Ibaka (OKC) bumps Mirotic (CHI) prior to the start of his shooting motion.
Westbrook's (OKC) shot attempt does not hit the rim and the shot clock expires. The game clock is reset to 00:04.9.
Westbrook (OKC) makes slight contact with Moore's (CHI) arm after he releases the ball, but does not affect his ability to follow-through. Westbrook gives Moore room to land.
After communicating with the Replay Center, the ruling on the court that Moore's (CHI) successful FGA was taken from behind the three-point line was confirmed.
Westbrook (OKC) steps OOB after catching the inbound pass.
Westbrook (OKC) commits a take foul on Mirotic (CHI).
